Semaphores
------------
in alloc when out of memory:
sem_post(&gc_semaphore);
sem_wait(&gc_semaphore);	

in rtgc_loop:
sem_wait(&gc_semaphore);
full_gc();
sem_post(&gc_semaphore);
------------

try gdb non-stop mode. Default is all-stop mode.
